lead_paragraph: The Steamship Prometheus Captain HENRY CHURCHILL, arrived at this port, on Saturday after noon, from Son Juan de Nicaragua, with news from California to the 6th September, the passage having been made from California, over the Nicaragua route, in the unparalleled short time of twenty-eight days.
abstract: No chance of re-election as Senator
